{"tid":432382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英人權領袖今午被拒入境  意味一國兩制已死","createTime":"2017-10-11T12:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T12:14:31.000Z","uid":70985,"like":5,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2da4a3b4622a59ae3d1c933fac04b20f4b66e6b4","tid":432382,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T12:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171011/large/1507705793_c90c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171011%2Flarge%2F1507705793_c90c.jpg&h=cfece5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾聲援被判囚的雙學三子、英國保守黨人權委員會副主席Benedict Rogers，外電報道指他今早從泰國曼谷抵港時，被拒絕入境，入境處並無交代原因。Benedict Rogers一直關注亞洲多國的人權狀況，今年8月曾在倫敦組織聲援黃之鋒、羅冠聰及周永康的行動，又曾批評英國政府作為《中英聯合聲明》簽署國，一直未有盡力為香港發聲，過去一直被中方視為眼中釘。他今午接受英國《衞報》訪問時表示，對被拒入境感到震驚，但坦言過去已有人警告過他遲早會被拒入境，認為今次是另一事例反映一國兩制正步向死亡。<br />\n<br />\nRogers曾於1997年至2002年在香港定居，今次訪港是除了與朋友會面，亦會了解香港最新的民主狀況。他向《衞報》記者稱，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當入境處職員押解他上機離境時，他曾問對方是否意味一國兩制已死，他指該入境處職員幾乎眼泛淚光，表情哀傷，只回覆他是在履行職務，無法回應，Rogers坦言為香港感到非常悲哀</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171011/57318427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171011%2F57318427&d=ToG9cpkj6Vi99OCoKNxotk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f95453c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171011%2F57318427&h=3174f207\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171011/57318427</a>"},{"pid":"6e17619643155f82d0372f064d41194286dff5b6","tid":432382,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"一般入境處職員會識佢係邊個？"},{"pid":"bfef1b207c5b67894dcb755b7010dd0f4656d34d","tid":432382,"uid":16970,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一般入境處職員會識佢係邊個？</blockquote><br />\n個入境押得佢上機, 會唔知佢係邊個?"},{"pid":"3c27c227ddc2c70c44c9610fd93b2b994db739a2","tid":432382,"uid":95617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0270a434329ce94e137863c82f555813e0946a90","tid":432382,"uid":95617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"一國兩制有開始過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4abd5f9bfee6aa5482ae590a1bec07cff0cb88b","tid":432382,"uid":17008,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:17:39.000Z","msg":"林鄭親自下達唔奇<br />\n條婆娘鐘意格硬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2be32e2934476b7ab88cb20c4438b9eb7580e24","tid":432382,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林鄭親自下達唔奇<br />\n條婆娘鐘意格硬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec3a21d6def98a3240a3d27f01e496333b1e98d","tid":432382,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cca7bfd86bbdfbed5b981d61ae3f119309c4927","tid":432382,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7d7903987095366396aabd4133938906f26522","tid":432382,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"去泰國做咩呢"},{"pid":"2c213e5a1f36702614727f36acfecec7d085d42c","tid":432382,"uid":42751,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:20:25.000Z","msg":"英國政府應該即時驅逐所有在英國留學的港人"},{"pid":"9e19f0ed18c1404f04d63fbed006380f2027f6d1","tid":432382,"uid":37413,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"c